		(property "Description_1" "The ESP32-S3-DEVKITC-1U-N8R8 from Espressif Systems is an evaluation board designed for wireless communication applications. It features a 32-bit Xtensa dual-core processor running at 240MHz, providing strong processing power for complex tasks. The board supports 802.11 b/g/n Wi-Fi and Bluetooth® 5.x (BLE), operating at 2.4GHz, ensuring seamless wireless communication."
